  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>This video showcase creating a Repair Ticket, including:\u00a0</p><ul><li><p>Attach a customer</p></li><li><p>Adding a repair device</p></li><li><p>Diagnostics, estimate, and logistics</p></li><li><p>Adding ticket items: services, parts, retail, etc.</p></li><li><p>Transactions</p></li><li><p>Custom forms</p></li><li><p>Advancing the ticket status</p></li><li><p>RMAs, defective/damaged parts</p></li></ul><a class=\"external-link\" data-card-appearance=\"embed\" data-layout=\"center\" data-original-height=\"480.00\" data-original-width=\"853.34\" data-width=\"100.00\" href=\"https://youtu.be/u2iudLUCE3o\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://youtu.be/u2iudLUCE3o</a><h2 id=\"CreatingaRepairTicket(video)-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h2><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933312070/Managing+Customer+Profiles\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933312070\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Managing Customer Profiles</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933639827/Assign+a+Virtual+Cash+Terminal+VCT+to+Accept+Payments\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933639827\" data-linked-resource-version=\"22\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Starting a Virtual Cash Terminal (VCT) to Accept Payments</a> </p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932460163/RMA+Process+Initiate+an+RMA+From+a+Ticket\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932460163\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">RMA Process: Initiate an RMA From a Ticket</a> </p></li></ul><p />",
